     H            Y.
     F** ADKR9C *******************************************************
     F*つるべ生産指示パラメータの日付以降の直接入力・臨時分を検索
     F*  2020.7.14
     F*****************************************************************
     FADKPP15 IF  E           K        DISK
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80WKZEHZ
     I                                        1   40WKZEYY
     I                                        5   60WKZEMM
     I                                        7   80WKZEDD
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80WKTOHZ
     I                                        1   40WKTOYY
     I                                        5   60WKTOMM
     I                                        7   80WKTODD
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1  100D1AP
     I                                        1   80D1APHZ
     I                                        9  100D1APBN
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1  100WKAP
     I                                        1   80WKAPHZ
     I                                        9  100WKAPBN
      *
     I           SDS
     I                                      254 263 @@USER
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           P1SHN1  5
     C                     PARM           P1SHN2  5
     C                     PARM           P1SHN3  2
     C                     PARM           P1TYPE  2
     C                     PARM           P1APHZ  80
     C                     PARM           P1APBN  20
     C                     PARM           P9MAIS  50
      *
     C                     Z-ADD0         WKAP
     C                     CALL 'ADKR95'
     C                     PARM           P#APHZ  80
     C                     PARM           P#APBN  20
     C                     Z-ADDP#APHZ    WKAPHZ
     C                     Z-ADDP#APBN    WKAPBN
      *
     C           KEY1      KLIST
     C                     KFLD           #KSHN1  5
     C                     KFLD           #KSHN2  5
     C                     KFLD           #KSHN3  2
     C                     KFLD           #KAPHZ  80
     C                     KFLD           #KAPBN  20
     C           KEY2      KLIST
     C                     KFLD           #KSHN1  5
     C                     KFLD           #KSHN2  5
     C                     KFLD           #KSHN3  2
     C                     MOVELP1SHN1    #KSHN1
     C                     MOVELP1SHN2    #KSHN2
     C                     MOVELP1SHN3    #KSHN3
     C                     Z-ADDP1APHZ    #KAPHZ
     C                     Z-ADDP1APBN    #KAPBN
     C                     Z-ADD0         P9MAIS
      *パラメータの日付・便でセットして
      *それ以降を品番で読む
     C           KEY1      SETLLADKPP151
     C           KEY2      READEADKPP151                 80
     C           *IN80     DOWEQ'0'
     C           D1SKJY    IFEQ 'D'
     C           D1SKHZ    ANDLE*DATE
     C                     ELSE
     C           D1TYPE    IFEQ P1TYPE
     C           D1AP      ANDLTWKAP
     C                     ADD  D1MAIS    P9MAIS
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
     C           KEY2      READEADKPP151                 80
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
